%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manoj%20says%20the%20hype%20around%20the%20big%20budgets%20of%20movies%20like%20'Ramayana'%2C%20Varanasi'%20is%20a%20PR%20tactic%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780577138000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131507796%2Cimgsize-48076.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmanoj-bajpayee-says-the-hype-around-the-big-budgets-of-movies-like-ramayana-varanasi-is-a-pr-tactic-these-rs-500-600-crore-that-they-are-talking-about-%2Farticleshow%2F131507726.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131507726.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EActor%20Manoj%20Bajpayee%20believes%20soaring%20film%20budgets%20are%20merely%20a%20publicity%20tactic%2C%20urging%20audiences%20to%20focus%20on%20content%20over%20financial%20figures.%20He%20highlighted%20that%20discussions%20about%20box%20office%20numbers%20distract%20from%20the%20viewing%20experience%2C%20as%20the%20money%20doesn't%20benefit%20the%20audience.%20Meanwhile%2C%20films%20like%20'Ramayana'%20and%20'Varanasi'%20are%20generating%20buzz%20with%20reportedly%20massive%20budgets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20son%20and%20grandson%20live%20in%20a%20tiny%20home%20on%20my%20property.%20In%20my%20retirement%2C%20I%20now%20homeschool%20my%20grandson.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221212%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Annie%20Nicol's%20tiny%20home%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2073642e5a80cfe05032a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnnie%20Nicol%20is%20homeschooling%20her%20grandson%2C%20who%20lives%20with%20her%20son%20in%20a%20tiny%20home%20on%20her%20property.%3Cp%3EAnnie%20Nicol%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Annie%20Nicol%2C%2076%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Petaluma%2C%20California.%20Nicol%20is%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplanned-homeschool-changed-mind-montessori-parenting-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehomeschooling%20her%20grandson%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20who%20lives%20with%20her%20son%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-term-care-tiny-home-trailer-assisted-living-independence-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Etiny%20home%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20on%20her%20property.%20It%20helps%20them%20stay%20close-knit%20and%20financially%20within%20their%20means.%20This%20interview%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20trend%20in%20our%20family%20that%20we%20take%20care%20of%20our%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20parents%2C%20who%20both%20lived%20into%20their%2090s%2C%20were%20retired%20educators%20and%20played%20a%20big%20role%20in%20caring%20for%20my%20kids.%20My%20son%20and%20I%20shared%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaregiving-work-life-balance-manager-caring-for-mom-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecaregiving%20responsibilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20them.%20My%20husband%20is%2080%20and%20works%20part-time%20as%20a%20therapist%2C%20and%20he%20takes%20care%20of%20his%20grandkids%20every%20Friday%20and%20on%20some%20Tuesdays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20grandson%2C%20who%20lives%20with%20me%2C%20lost%20his%20mother%20when%20he%20was%20an%20infant.%20He%20has%20an%20auntie%20he's%20very%20close%20to%2C%20but%20it%20took%20some%20time%20because%20she%20lives%20out%20of%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2280220294-9c6f-4128-84b8-ecd00ff83ab8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20son%20and%20grandson%20live%20near%20my%20husband%20and%20me%20in%20a%20tiny%20house%20next%20door%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20and%20grandson%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiny-living-taught-me-how-to-save-money-better-consumer-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etiny%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20property.%20The%20building%20was%20there%20when%20I%20moved%20here%2042%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20it%20was%20showing%20its%20age%20then.%20The%20knob%20and%20tube%20electricity%20present%20when%20I%20purchased%20the%20house%20was%20common%20in%20homes%20built%20between%201880%20and%201940.%20The%20main%20old%20farmhouse%20was%20built%20over%20100%20years%20ago.%20I%20imagine%20the%20outbuilding%20was%20built%20around%20the%20same%20time.%20The%20repurposed%20space%20outside%20is%20adjacent%20to%20the%20main%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20and%20grandson%20basically%20have%20a%20bunkhouse%2C%20which%20includes%20my%20son's%20workshop.%20It's%20maybe%20200%20square%20feet%20total%20and%20about%2015%20feet%20from%20our%20back%20door.%20The%20bathroom%20and%20kitchen%20are%20inside%20the%20main%20house.%20My%20grandson%20has%20a%20bedroom%20in%20the%20main%20house%2C%20too%2C%20where%20he%20keeps%20his%20trains%2C%20Lego%20bricks%2C%20and%20school%20work.%20He%20prefers%20to%20bunk%20close%20to%20his%20dad%20in%20the%20outbuilding%20at%20this%20time.%20We%20all%20eat%20dinner%20together%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d2ab931-0f20-4c10-883b-219965377fc0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20retired%20at%2075%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226964%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Annie%20Nicol%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a20708f2ab5f9757add8da7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224643%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnnie%20Nicol%20retired%20at%2075%20and%20spends%20her%20time%20caring%20for%20her%20grandson.%3Cp%3EMike%20Kai%20Chen%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20retired%20nurse%20practitioner.%20I%20went%20into%20nursing%20instead%20of%20medicine%20partly%20because%20of%20a%20divorce%20and%20needing%20more%20flexibility%20in%20my%20life%2C%20especially%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fraising-kids-abroad-elderly-care-mom-back-home-sandwich-generation-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaking%20care%20of%20my%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I've%20worked%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20substance%20use%20and%20community%20health%20centers.%20I%20developed%20a%20clinic%20within%20a%20shelter%20in%20my%20town%2C%20which%20is%20still%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20children%20were%20small%2C%20we%20would%20go%20camping%20all%20over%20California.%20When%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-we-learned-from-americas-oldest-workers-80-over-80-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworked%20full-time%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20that%20flexibility.%20I%20wish%20I%20could%20have%20kept%20this%20up%20a%20little%20longer%2C%20but%20financially%2C%20I%20had%20to%20be%20careful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20perhaps%20would%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-increase-savings-early-retirement-expenses-financial-freedom-fire-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretired%20sooner%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20COVID%20not%20hit.%20The%20support%20structures%20were%20somewhat%20destroyed%2C%20and%20people%20were%20afraid.%20I%20felt%20I%20needed%20to%20mentor%20some%20of%20the%20people%20who%20would%20be%20taking%20over%20my%20position.%20I%20love%20my%20patients%2C%20and%20I've%20had%20some%20for%20almost%20their%20whole%20lives.%20I%20got%20as%20much%20as%20I%20gave.%20I%20retired%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bbe3752-ae47-4b64-b576-14e6472bff64%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20became%20my%20grandson's%20homeschool%20teacher.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20was%20working%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcant-retire-grandparents-raising-grandchildren-gas-prices-social-security-costs-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelped%20my%20grandson%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%20schooling%20at%20least%20three%20days%20a%20week%20because%20it%20was%20interrupted%20during%20COVID.%20He%20has%20another%20set%20of%20grandparents%20who%20live%20outside%20our%20community%20and%20wanted%20to%20be%20involved.%20Hence%2C%20we%20started%20doing%20the%20homeschool%20thing%2C%20splitting%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Annie%20Nicol%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b1969fa7a4f9df67ba2831%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnnie%20Nicol%20said%20she's%20valued%20seeing%20the%20spark%20in%20her%20grandson's%20eyes%20when%20teaching%20him.%3Cp%3EMike%20Kai%20Chen%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20other%20grandma%2C%20who%20was%20a%20teacher%2C%20and%20his%20auntie%2C%20also%20a%20teacher%2C%20would%20come%20down%20from%20their%20community%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskills-based-volunteer-programs-boost-employee-satisfaction-engagement-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evolunteer%20one%20day%20a%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20his%20school.%20They%20really%20wanted%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20their%20daughter's%20son's%20life.%20The%20other%20grandpa%20set%20this%20up%2C%20with%20a%20homeschool%20supervisor-teacher%20who%20manages%20the%20curriculum%20to%20meet%20California's%20standards.%20I%20do%20what's%20called%20Studies%20Weekly%2C%20which%20uses%20a%20somewhat%20Socratic%20method.%20You're%20looking%20for%20a%20deeper%20response%20rather%20than%20just%20spitting%20out%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20commitment%20started%20with%20a%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20do%20this.%26quot%3B%20I%20appreciated%20what%20he%20was%20learning%2C%20and%20it%20helped%20me%20learn%20new%20things%20and%20understand%20his%20needs.%20It's%20really%20fun%20to%20see%20when%20he%20is%20engaged%20and%20by%20what.%20It's%20kind%20of%20what%20I%20did%20when%20I%20was%20somewhat%20teaching%20my%20patients.%20I'd%20look%20for%20that%20glimmer%20in%20their%20eyes%20that%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20got%20it.%26quot%3B%20When%20he%20rolls%20his%20eyes%20or%20looks%20the%20other%20way%2C%20I%20see%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20his%20attention.%20It's%20important%20for%20me%20to%20know%20that%20he's%20grasped%20the%20concepts.%20It's%20giving%2C%20taking%2C%20and%20sharing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2221f243e7-382b-423a-89d9-e4009b1cab8d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20tried%20to%20be%20as%20involved%20as%20I%20can%20in%20my%20grandchildren's%20lives.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20daughter%20who%20lives%20in%20Santa%20Barbara%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20see%20her%20three%20kids%20as%20much.%20Still%2C%20they%20would%20call%20me%20Grandma%20Airport%20because%20I'd%20always%20arrive%20at%20the%20airport%20instead%20of%20a%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20certain%20extent%2C%20I%20contribute%20what%20I%20can%20for%20birthdays%20and%20gifts.%20My%20son%20has%20a%20house%20that%20he's%20not%20living%20in%20and%20is%20rented%20out%2C%20so%20I'll%20help%20with%20that.%20For%20the%20other%20kids%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20funding%20goes%20toward%20things%20like%20museum%20or%20theater%20tickets.%20I'm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-disneyland-trip-tips-mistakes-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaking%20my%20grandson%20to%20Disneyland%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20I%20haven't%20been%20to%20in%2030%20years%2C%20or%20I'll%20visit%20my%20granddaughter%20in%20Hawaii.%20I'm%20also%20putting%20some%20funds%20toward%20experiences%20that%20help%20them%20engage%20in%20other%20forms%20of%20education%2C%20and%20I'm%20putting%20money%20aside%20for%20them%20when%20I%20die%20so%20they'll%20have%20some%20help%20with%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Annie%20Nicol%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a207031b4fb977f359841e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnnie%20Nicol%20spends%20some%20of%20her%20time%20tending%20to%20her%20sheep.%3Cp%3EMike%20Kai%20Chen%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20spend%20my%20time%20going%20through%20boxes%20of%20my%20parents'%20belongings.%20They%20died%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20but%20my%20mom%20was%20a%20writer%20and%20wrote%20a%20tremendous%20amount.%20I%20am%20also%20on%20a%20local%20board%20focused%20on%20our%20unhoused%20population%20and%20do%20whatever%20I%20can%20to%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20live%20on%20three%20acres%20and%20have%20a%20small%20farm%20that%20grows%20a%20lot%20of%20vegetables.%20We%20have%20sheep%2C%20too.%20I%20love%20working%20in%20the%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20live%20frugally%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20too%20worried.%20I%20own%20three%20properties%2C%20so%20if%20push%20comes%20to%20shove%2C%20I%20can%20sell%20them.%20I've%20always%20been%20careful%20and%20don't%20buy%20anything%20that's%20expensive.%20I%20go%20out%20to%20eat%20maybe%20once%20a%20month.%20The%20biggest%20financial%20issue%20right%20now%20is%20that%20my%20century-old%20house%20needs%20a%20lot%20of%20repairs%2C%20so%20I'm%20trying%20to%20strategize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-tiny-home-grandparents-raising-grandchildren-caregiving-cost-savings-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780577041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a207055b4fb977f359841e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-tiny-home-grandparents-raising-grandchildren-caregiving-cost-savings-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Annie%20Nicol%2C%2076%2C%20i