0compact%20enough%20for%20my%20space%20and%20comfortable%20enough%20for%20the%20way%20I%20actually%20live%3A%20reading%2C%20working%2C%20watching%20baseball%2C%20and%20sprawling%20out%20with%20my%20senior%20chihuahua.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20looking%20for%20something%20made%20with%20higher-quality%2C%20PFAS-free%20materials.%20As%20a%20cancer%20survivor%20with%20skin%20sensitivities%20and%20lingering%20respiratory%20symptoms%2C%20I've%20become%20more%20mindful%20about%20the%20fabrics%20and%20foams%20I%20bring%20into%20my%20home.%20That's%20what%20led%20me%20to%20Sabai%2C%20and%20eventually%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3Dac8cb5581d345e6f4ba7ea032b4ef52211e05efb843150e4f2f5faa6da02b9a7%26postID%3D6a1f49857fe520cd1140c422%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fsabai-eclipse-sleeper-sofa-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526amp%253Burl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fsabai.design%25252Fproducts%25252Fthe-eclipse-90-sleeper-sofa-in-recycled-velvet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESabai%20Eclipse%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20funky%2C%20chunky%2C%20colorful%20sleeper%20sofa%20that%20looks%20like%20a%20statement%20couch%20first%20and%20a%20guest%20bed%20second.%20It's%20rare%20that%20I%20actually%20like%20the%20look%20of%20a%20sleeper%20in%20its%20couch%20form.%20Suddenly%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20an%20additional%20bed%20in%20my%20living%20room%20felt%20like%20it%20would%20be%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20movie%20nights%2C%20friend%20sleepovers%2C%20and%20yes%2C%20I%20suppose%2C%20the%20occasional%20out-of-town%20guest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20month%20with%20the%2090-inch%20Eclipse%2C%20including%20three%20nights%20sleeping%20on%20it%20in%20bed%20mode%2C%20it%20has%20become%20my%20favorite%20place%20to%20hang%20out%20in%20my%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eb448e77-dfb2-4886-a393-4e6468d2e303%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20is%20the%20Sabai%20Eclipse%20Sleeper%20Sofa%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Sabai%20Eclipse%20Sleeper%20Sofa%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22orange%20velvet%20sabai%20sofa%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2081b2b4fb977f35984286%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%2090-inch%20Sabai%20Eclipse%20is%20available%20in%20three%20upholstery%20options%20across%2035%20colors%2C%20including%20options%20with%20contrast%20piping.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Yagoda%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESabai%20released%20the%20Eclipse%20Sleeper%20in%20response%20to%20customer%20feedback%20about%20an%20interest%20in%20a%20sleeper%20sofa%20without%20a%20metal%20mechanism.%20The%2090-inch%20version%2C%20which%20I%20tested%2C%20comfortably%20fits%20three%20and%20transitions%20into%20a%20queen-size%20bed.%20The%20sofa%20is%20also%20available%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D723fc34b7775c36c4d6b4517c0bcf902ea8c24598ed12860c1566ce406b4df9e%26postID%3D6a1f49857fe520cd1140c422%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fsabai-eclipse-sleeper-sofa-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526amp%253Burl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fsabai.design%25252Fproducts%25252Fthe-eclipse-sofa-in-recycled-velvet%25253Fvariant%25253D51909027594603%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E70-inch%3C%2Fa%3E%20queen%20two-seater%20for%20smaller%20spaces%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D5b12c3ece26d885f83f72bff9d43f008e23fe7f68904aced129a325d78f08ee6%26postID%3D6a1f49857fe520cd1140c422%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fsabai-eclipse-sleeper-sofa-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526amp%253Burl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fsabai.design%25252Fproducts%25252Fthe-eclipse-chair-in-recycled-velvet%25253Fvariant%25253D51926348988779%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwin%20XL%3C%2Fa%3E%20sleeper%20chair.%20The%20sizing%20differences%20are%20important%20to%20note%2C%20as%20it's%20not%20just%20two%20sofas%2C%20with%20one%20being%20shorter%20than%20the%20other.%20The%2090%20inch%20has%20a%20shallower%20depth%20of%2034%20inches%20(23%20inch%20seat%20depth)%20and%20requires%20less%20floor%20space%20to%20expand%3B%20the%2070-inch%20design%20is%20deeper%20at%2044-inch%20depth%20(33-inch%20seat%20depth)%20and%20flips%20out%20further.%20Both%20convert%20to%20queen%20sizes%20mattress%2C%20with%20the%2090%20inch%20version%2C%20you%20sleep%20horizontally%20across%2C%20while%20the%2070-inch%20your%20head%20rests%20against%20the%20back%20cushions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20want%20to%20reiterate%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20sad%20beige%20futon%20of%20sleepers%20past.%20It%20looks%20like%20a%20real%20couch%20first%2C%20and%20a%20sleeper%20second%20%E2%80%94%20exactly%20what%20I%20want%20for%20a%20piece%20that%20I'll%20keep%20in%20couch%20form%2090%25%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Eclipse%20has%20a%20rounded%2C%20statement%20look%20that%20sets%20it%20apart%20from%20many%20sleeper%20sofas.%20It%20comes%20in%20three%20upholstery%20options%20%E2%80%94%20upcycled%20poly%2C%20hemp%20blend%2C%20and%20recycled%20velvet%20%E2%80%94%20across%20more%20than%2035%20colors%2C%20including%20stripes%20and%20contrast%20piping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20colors%20are%20exceptionally%20vibrant%2C%20modern%2C%20and%20distinctive-looking%2C%20with%20hues%20and%20combinations%20you%20don't%20see%20everywhere%20(indigo%20with%20amber%20piping%20or%20cornflower%20with%20mustard%20piping!).%20I%20chose%20recycled%20velvet%20in%20amber%20with%20chocolate%20piping%20after%20ordering%20free%20swatches%2C%20which%20I%20highly%20recommend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20I've%20been%20eager%20to%20break%20free%20from%20the%20%26quot%3Bfast%20furniture%26quot%3B%20cycle.%20Sabai%20also%20appealed%20to%20me%20because%20it's%20designed%20to%20be%20repaired%20rather%20than%20replaced.%20The%20brand%20sells%20individual%20parts%2C%20including%20cushion%20inserts%2C%20sofa%20arms%2C%20and%20slipcovers%2C%20and%20its%20expansion%20kits%20let%20you%20turn%20some%20sofas%20into%20sectionals%20if%20your%20space%20changes.%20Of%20note%2C%20Sabai%20uses%20mechanical%20fasteners%2C%20not%20permanent%20glues%2C%20so%20components%20can%20easily%20be%20replaced%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESabai%20offers%20returns%20within%2030%20days%20of%20delivery%2C%20but%20deducts%20a%2010%25%20return%20processing%20fee%20or%2015%25%20if%20you%20don't%20keep%20the%20original%20boxes.%20It%20backs%20its%20products%20with%20a%20one-year%20warranty%2C%20and%20they%20offer%20an%20optional%20two-year%20product%20protection%20package%20that%20covers%20things%20like%20spills%20and%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22974ae1b9-0f85-4a90-b632-d19a9244f6d9%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Delivery%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelivery%20and%20assembly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20ordering%20to%20delivery%2C%20the%20process%20took%20exactly%20one%20month.%20Shipping%20varies%20according%20to%20what%20you%20purchase%20at%20Sabai%2C%20but%20it%20is%20%24195%20for%20standard%20delivery%20or%20%24245%20for%20White%20Glove%20Delivery%2C%20which%20includes%20assembly.%20It's%20just%20a%20%2450%20difference%20for%20a%20hands-off%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20white-glove%20delivery%20process%20was%20smooth%2C%20with%20clear%20communication%20throughout.%20The%20service%20that%20Sabai%20works%20with%20called%20me%20the%20week%20of%20the%20delivery%20to%20coordinate%20a%20day%20and%20timeframe%20for%20delivery.%20During%20that%20exact%20window%2C%20a%20team%20of%20three%20men%20arrived%20and%20quickly%20got%20to%20work%20assembling%20the%20couch%3B%20from%20start%20to%20finish%2C%20the%20whole%20process%20took%2030%20minutes.%20And%20once%20they%20left%2C%20and%20I%20flopped%20down%20on%20it%2C%20the%20couch%20felt%20extremely%20sturdy%20and%20sound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20customers%20assemble%20the%20Eclipse%20themselves%3B%20it%20arrives%20in%20four%20boxes%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsabai.design%2Fpages%2Fassembly-instructions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonline%20instructions%3C%2Fa%3E%20(as%20opposed%20to%20printed%20in%20the%20box).%20They%20looked%20straightforward%2C%20though%20I'd%20want%20a%20second%20person%20to%20help.%20Sabai%20says%20its%20average%20shipping%20time%20is%20three%20to%20five%20weeks%2C%20with%20some%20colors%20noting%20a%20couple%20extra%20weeks%20for%20shipping.%20However%2C%20some%20online%20reviewers%20have%20reported%20waiting%20over%20two%20months%20to%20receive%20their%20couches.%20Given%20that%20the%20pieces%20are%20custom-made%2C%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20greater%20variability%20in%20delivery%20times%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22988fe18c-8ae6-4347-8109-f2cf09c26be4%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22First%20impressions%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%20impressions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20away%2C%20I%20love%20how%20chunky%20and%20plush%20the%20couch%20looks%20and%20feels.%20The%20deep%2C%20sculptural%20cushions%20are%20medium-firm%20and%20offer%20a%20nice%20balance%20of%20bounce%20and%20support.%20The%20amber-chocolate%20fabric-piping%20combo%20is%20even%20more%20vibrant%20in%20person%20and%20immediately%20became%20the%20center%20piece%20of%20my%20living%20room.%20It's%20undeniably%20a%20statement%20piece%2C%20but%20one%20I%20quickly%20feel%20comfortable%20being%20messy%20and%20lazy%20on.%20My%20dog%20started%20digging%20on%20it%20immediately%2C%20and%20the%20fabric%20still%20doesn't%20show%20any%20tears%20or%20scratches.%20(Though%20the%20dog%20hair%20does%20start%20to%20accumulate%2C%20it%20easily%20vacuums%20off.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ecdcccb0-33f5-4479-92d0-2d7885a1e76e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Sitting%20comfort%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESitting%20comfort%3A%20plush%2C%20deep%2C%20and%20loungey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20of%20a%20dog%20on%20a%20orange%20velvet%20sofa%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2083912ab5f9757add8e43%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sabai%20Eclipse%20has%20a%20deep-seated%20design%20that%20makes%20it%20ideal%20for%20lounging%2C%20and%20perfectly%20wide%20enough%20to%20sprawl%20out%20together%20with%20my%20dog.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Yagoda%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20couch%20form%2C%20the%20Eclipse%20is%20really%20plush%20and%20cozy%2C%20with%20the%20cushions%20offering%20enough%20support%20that%20you%20don't%20feel%20like%20you're%20melting%2C%20but%20not%20so%20stiff%20you%20can't%20relax.%20Even%20though%20the%20piece%20takes%20up%20a%20substantial%20amount%20of%20my%20small%20Brooklyn%20living%20room%2C%20I%20appreciate%20how%20deep%20it%20is%3A%20the%20cushions%20are%2023%20inches%20deep%2C%20which%20gives%20me%20enough%20room%20to%20sit%20cross-legged%20or%20lie%20side%20by%20side%20with%20my%20dog%20while%20watching%20TV.%20The%20trade-off%20is%20that%20it's%20not%20especially%20well-suited%20to%20working%20or%20sitting%20upright%20for%20long%20stretches.%20When%20I%20sit%20with%20my%20feet%20flat%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20my%20back%20doesn't%20naturally%20reach%20the%20back%20cushions%3B%20when%20I%20scoot%20all%20the%20way%20back%2C%20my%20feet%20don't%20comfortably%20touch%20the%20floor.%20I%20tend%20to%20slouch%20as%20a%20result%2C%20which%20can%20start%20to%20irritate%20my%20shoulders%20after%20a%20while.%20This%20isn't%20a%20major%20issue%20for%20me%2C%20since%20I%20spend%20most%20of%20the%20day%20working%20at%20my%20desk%20or%20sitting%20cross-legged%20on%20the%20sofa%2C%20but%20I%20usually%20need%20an%20extra%20throw%20pillow%20for%20back%20support%20if%20I'm%20sitting%20upright%20for%20several%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20cushions%20are%20extremely%20plush%2C%20and%20the%20recycled-velvet%20feels%20very%20luxurious%20against%20the%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20adults%20can%20fit%20really%20comfortably%20on%20it.%20But%20even%20better%2C%20I%20can%20lie%20down%20on%20the%20couch%20for%20a%20nap%20without%20even%20having%20to%20convert%20it%20to%20a%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a287106-96b7-41ea-9083-1c6d5c348f34%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Sleeping%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESleeping%20comfort%3A%20Is%20it%20actually%20good%20for%20guests%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20dog%20on%20a%20sofa%20bed%20made%20out%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2044582ab5f9757add875f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20the%2090-inch%20Eclipse%2C%20you%20sleep%20horizontally%20along%20the%20length%20of%20the%20sofa%2C%20which%20takes%20up%20less%20floor%20space.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Yagoda%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conversion%20style%20is%20manual%20fold-out%2C%20which%20takes%20literally%20less%20than%2030%20seconds%20to%20set%20up.%20(Sabai%20promises%20less%20than%205%20minutes%2C%20but%20it%20takes%20me%20less%20than%20a%20minute.)%20Once%20I%20make%20the%20bed%20with%20sheets%2C%20I'm%20still%20only%20at%202%20and%20a%20half%20minutes.%20I%20love%20that%20one%20person%20can%20easily%20open%20and%20set%20up%20the%20bed%3A%20you%20just%20take%20off%20the%20back%20cushions%2C%20and%20then%20fold%20out%20the%20seat%20cushions%20into%20the%20mattress.%20There%20are%20handles%20on%20the%20cushions%20to%20help%20with%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22pulling%20out%20an%20orange%20sofa%20bed%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2044582ab5f9757add8760%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20you%20remove%20the%20back%20cushions%2C%20just%20used%20the%20attached%20handles%20to%20fold%20out%20the%20mattress.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Yagoda%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mattress%20itself%20is%20medium-firm%20with%20that%20nice%20foam%20cushiness%20and%20no%20uncomfy%20metal%20bars%20or%20creakiness.%20The%20bed%20is%20stable%20and%20secure%2C%20and%20I%20find%20it%20offers%20enough%20support%20that%20a%20mattress%20topper%20isn't%20needed.%20Sheets%20fit%20easily%20around%20it.%20Because%20the%20bed%20is%20a%20fold-out%2C%20there%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20little%20groove%20in%20the%20middle%20between%20the%20two%20cushions%20that%20fold%20together%20to%20form%20the%20seat%20of%20the%20couch.%20So%20if%20you%20sleep%20directly%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20bed%20(I%20don't%2C%20I%20always%20choose%20a%20side)%2C%20you%20might%20want%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20mattress%20topper%20to%20cover%20it.%20But%20with%20two%20evenly%20spaced%20adults%2C%20that%20small%20middle%20groove%20is%20a%20non-issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sabai%20sofa%20folded%20out%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2081b22e5a80cfe050331f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20sofa%20bed%20once%20it%20is%20flipped%20out.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Yagoda%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20most%20important%20metric%2C%20sleep%20quality%2C%20my%20chihuahua%20and%20I%20slept%20on%20the%20bed%20for%20three%20nights%20during%20testing%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20wake%20up%20with%20any%20nagging%20back%20discomfort%20or%20soreness.%20The%20medium-firm%20foam%20is%20an%20excellent%20match%20with%20my%20sleep%20personality%2C%20and%20it's%20kind%20of%20fun%20to%20be%20so%20close%20to%20the%20floor%20(something%20I%20enjoy%20about%20many%20beds%20in%20Japan).%20I%20definitely%20plan%20on%20having%20sleepovers%20on%20it%20in%20the%20future.%20Folding%20it%20back%20up%20and%20returning%20it%20to%20couch%20form%20took%20less%20than%20a%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2248c2b485-46d2-44ad-afd5-d51217125cad%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Durability%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%20and%20everyday%20use%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22close%20up%20of%20sabai%20orange%20sofa%20upholstery%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2081b22e5a80cfe050331e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDespite%20my%20dog's%20constant%20digging%20and%20scratching%2C%20the%20sofa%20itself%20is%20unscathed%2C%20though%20velvet%20is%20a%20magnet%20for%20pet%20hair.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Yagoda%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20month%20of%20eating%2C%20drinking%2C%20napping%2C%20and%20burying%20socks%20(my%20dog)%20on%20this%20couch%2C%20the%20piece%20still%20looks%20clean%20and%20vibrant.%20Dog%20hairs%20accumulate%20on%20it%2C%20but%20no%20more%20than%20any%20single%20item%20in%20my%20house%2C%20and%20they%20come%20off%20easily%20with%20a%20lint%20roller%20and%20the%20vacuum.%20For%20small%20spills%2C%20spot-cleaning%20with%20water%20has%20done%20the%20trick%2C%20but%20I%20imagine%20I'll%20want%20to%20remove%20the%20covers%20and%20bring%20them%20to%20the%20laundromat%20at%20some%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I've%20mentioned%2C%20my%20dog%20is%20an%20aggressive%20digger%2C%20and%20digs%20on%20the%20couch%20every%20day%2C%20and%20so%20far%2C%20the%20velvet%20is%20none%20the%20worse%20for%20it.%20No%20tears%2C%20pilling%2C%20or%20visible%20scratches%E2%80%94somewhat%20miraculously.%20The%20fabric%20is%20still%20silky-soft%20and%20richly%20pigmented%2C%20even%20after%20my%20dog%20has%20scratched%20it%20incessantly%20every%20day%20for%2030%20days%20straight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20durability%20feels%20a%20step%20above%20all%20of%20my%20past%20couches.%20For%20one%2C%20there's%20no%20wobbling%2C%20groaning%2C%20or%20creaking%20when%20I%20toss%20my%20entire%20body%20on%20it%20dramatically.%20I%20really%20get%20the%20feeling%20that%20this%20is%20built%20to%20last%E2%80%94and%20it%20damn%20well%20should%20be%2C%20because%20that's%20what%20they're%20promising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c960ff0-dc5c-44bc-8cd0-7c0566e6177c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Eco-friendly%20materials%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20eco-friendly%20details%20that%20actually%20matter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESabai's%20sustainability%20claims%20are%20a%20major%20part%20of%20the%20appeal.%20The%20brand%20uses%20PFAS-free%20fabrics%20and%20FSC-certified%20wood%2C%20and%20offers%20three%20upholstery%20options%20all%20with%20a%20sustainability%20focus%3A%20recycled%20velvet%2C%20upcycled%20poly%2C%20and%20a%20hemp%20blend.%20My%20recycled%20velvet%20fabric%20is%20made%20from%20recycled%20water%20bottles%20and%20is%20OEKO-TEX%20certified.%20The%20upcycled%20poly%20is%20GreenGuard-Gold%20certified%20and%20made%20from%20100%25%20upcycled%20Olefin%2C%20a%20material%20that%20requires%20no%20land%20or%20water%20for%20production%2C%20while%20the%20organic%20hemp%20blend%20is%2055%25%20hemp%20and%2045%25%20cotton.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sofa%20also%20uses%20Cocolok%2C%20a%20rubberized%20coconut%20fiber%2C%20around%20the%20frame%20instead%20of%20polyester%20upholstery%20fiber.%20Sabai%20says%20it%20avoids%20polyurethane%20foam%2C%20a%20common%20material%20in%20upholstered%20furniture%20that%20can%20emit%20VOCs%2C%20which%20may%20irritate%20people%20with%20respiratory%20sensitivities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20importantly%2C%20the%20sofa%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20repaired.%20Sabai%20sells%20replacement%20parts%20and%20covers%2C%20offers%20expansion%20kits%20for%20some%20pieces%2C%20and%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsabai.design%2Fpages%2Fbuyback%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBuyBack%20Program%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20lets%20customers%20resell%20eligible%20sofas%20instead%20of%20sending%20them%20to%20a%20landfill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c4500568-052d-4903-b2a9-52cf97a6f003%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20I%20didn't%20like%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20I%20didn't%20like%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22close%20up%20of%20the%20ridge%20of%20a%20sofa%20bed%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2044582ab5f9757add8761%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere's%20a%20small%20divot%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20mattress%20where%20the%20mattress%20flips%20out.%20Here's%20how%20it%20looks%20when%20in%20place.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Yagoda%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20I%20didn't%20like%5C%22%3EThe%20main%20drawback%20is%20that%20the%20Eclipse%20is%20better%20for%20lounging%20than%20upright%20sitting.%20The%20deep%20seat%20can%20make%20working%20from%20the%20couch%20awkward%20without%20a%20back%20pillow.%20It%20also%20has%20no%20under-couch%20storage%2C%20and%20the%20mattress%20sits%20low%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20which%20may%20be%20difficult%20for%20guests%20with%20mobility%20issues.%20Finally%2C%20because%20Sabai%20pieces%20are%20custom-made%2C%20delivery%20can%20take%20several%20weeks%2C%20and%20some%20online%20reviewers%20report%20longer%20waits.%20This%20is%20in%20contrast%20to%20sites%20like%20Wayfair%20and%20Amazon%20have%20spoiled%20us%20with%20next-day%20delivery%20expectations%2C%20even%20on%20big-ticket%20items%20like%20chairs%20and%20couches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20point%20is%20also%20quite%20high%20compared%20to%20sleeper%20options%20from%20IKEA%2C%20Wayfair%2C%20and%20Target%2C%20but%20on%20par%20with%20other%20sleeper%20sofas%20from%20Interior%20Define%2C%20Joybird%2C%20or%20even%20West%20Elm%2C%20and%20maybe%20even%20less%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a94b8ff-ee1b-4d74-8906-984a41514800%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20your%20alternatives%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223008%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22koala%20sofa%20bed%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69dfecdb557731f181e95132%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222256%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Koala%20Sofa%20Bed%20is%20visually%20similar%20to%20Sabai's%20and%20folds%20outs%20to%20become%20a%20sleeper%20sofa%20in%20a%20similar%20way.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20Eclipse%2C%20Sabai%20also%20offers%20the%20slightly%20larger%2096-inch%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3Df951e44bf8080edcea524fcace0b2ae9b939cc60eadcbae3f0df393010d565b8%26postID%3D6a1f49857fe520cd1140c422%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fsabai-eclipse-sleeper-sofa-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526amp%253Burl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fsabai.design%25252Fproducts%25252Fthe-elevate-sofa-in-recycled-velvet%25253Fvariant%25253D45631310823584%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElevate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20converts%20into%20a%20sleeper%20sofa%20with%20a%20mattress-topper%20add-on%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D319f8cae10f9fadb14003fae247e54c30ac615e2b6efbe0c912ee05826ffd8d1%26postID%3D6a1f49857fe520cd1140c422%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fsabai-eclipse-sleeper-sofa-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526amp%253Burl%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fsabai.design%25252Fproducts%25252Fthe-essential-sofa-in-recycled-velvet%25253Fvariant%25253D43036480307360%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEssential%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20mid-century-inspired%20design%20with%20legs.%20In%20terms%20of%20appearance%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22h