20the%20time%20to%20brace%20for%20the%20impacts%2C%20calling%20on%20humanities%20and%20STEM%20students%20to%20adapt%20to%20the%20new%20era%20and%20%26quot%3Blean%20in%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSociety%20needs%20to%20hear%20that%20because%20we%20don't%20have%20long%20to%20prepare%20for%20what%20that%20means%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20future%2C%20in%20my%20view%2C%20is%20still%20to%20be%20written%2C%20but%20these%20next%20few%20years%20are%20going%20to%20be%20very%20critical%20as%20to%20which%20way%20that%20will%20go%20and%20how%20we%20collectively%20want%20that%20to%20look%20like.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-deepmind-ceo-demis-hassabis-agi-new-human-era-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780566361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a20cde5b4fb977f359843c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-deepmind-ceo-demis-hassabis-agi-new-human-era-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20DeepMind%20CEO%20Demis%20Hassabis%20said%20AGI%20is%20just%20a%20few%20years%20a%20way%20and%20that%20humanity%20doesn't%20have%20much%20time%20to%20prepare%20for%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Bengal%20Civic%20Volunteer%20Hides%20Under%20Bed%20To%20Evade%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22According%20to%20local%20sources%2C%20Shahidul%20Mia%20had%20allegedly%20been%20collecting%20money%20from%20people%20for%20a%20considerable%20period%2C%20claiming%20that%20he%20could%20help%20them%20secure%20houses%20under%20the%20government's%20housing%20programme%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780566195000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-06%2Fdmavae88