20and%20Grogu%26quot%3B%20this%20past%20weekend%20in%20ticket%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20build%20on%20an%20earlier%20box%20office%20darling%2C%20%26quot%3BIron%20Lung%2C%26quot%3B%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-markiplier-iron-lung-beats-amazon-melania-box-office-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EYouTuber%20%26quot%3BMarkiplier%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Mark%20Edward%20Fischbach)%2C%20and%20show%20how%20a%20digital%20creator%20with%20a%20small%20budget%20can%20draw%20movie%20theater%20crowds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHollywood%20is%20beginning%20to%20make%20bets%20on%20YouTube%20creators%2C%20and%20industry%20insiders%20say%20horror%20films%20like%20these%2C%20as%20well%20as%20comedy%2C%20will%20lead%20the%20way%20because%20they're%20cheaper%20to%20produce%20and%20can%20be%20box-office%20draws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELarge-scale%20investments%20remain%20rare%20due%20to%20the%20limited%20number%20of%20creators%20with%20proven%20directing%20and%20writing%20experience.%20In%20making%20the%20leap%20to%20film%2C%20follower%20counts%20don't%20always%20translate%20to%20Hollywood%20success%2C%20said%20Kai%20Gayoso%2C%20a%20managing%20partner%20at%20Range%20Media.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalent%20and%20storytelling%20chops%20carry%20more%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDigital%20media%20has%20produced%20TV%20stars%20like%20Issa%20Rae%20and%20hits%20like%20%26quot%3BBroad%20City.%26quot%3B%20As%20more%20filmmakers%20emerge%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-media-superstars-are-over-all-about-niche-creators-now-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20executives%20expect%20new%20ideas%20and%20franchises%20to%20originate%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20more%20turns%20at%20bat%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Adam%20Wescott%2C%20CEO%20of%20Mind%20Chatter%20Media%2C%20a%20digital%20media%20company%20and%20content%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20asked%20agents%2C%20media%20executives%2C%20YouTube%20editors%20and%20creators%2C%20and%20other%20industry%20insiders%20who%20could%20get%20a%20crack%20at%20the%20big%20screen%20next.%20Their%20picks%20represent%20a%20mix%20of%20people%20known%20for%20their%20work%20in%20comedy%2C%20scripted%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20is%20clear%20%E2%80%94%20Hollywood's%20next%20filmmakers%20may%20not%20be%20the%20biggest%20names%20now%2C%20but%20have%20been%20developing%20characters%2C%20worlds%2C%20and%20directing%20skills%20online%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224294fa1c-e094-4dc7-92d0-a70ab731af70%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20establishment%20players%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20obvious%20names%20are%20creators%20who%20have%20already%20crossed%20over%20to%20Hollywood%20with%20streaming%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFox%20Corporation's%20Tubi%20courted%20%3Cstrong%3EKinigra%20Deon%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebehind%20scripted%20YouTube%20shows%20like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Hairshop%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20direct%20the%20film%20%26quot%3BSundown%26quot%3B%20this%20year%20through%20a%20deal%20with%20Kevin%20Hart's%20Hartbeat.%20%3Cstrong%3EGray%20Fagan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0released%20a%20high-school%20comedy%2C%20%26quot%3BSenior%20Prank%2C%26quot%3B%20on%20Tubi%20and%20is%20working%20on%20a%20comedy%20horror.%20TikTok%20comedian%20%3Cstrong%3EKelon%20Campbell%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20who%20goes%20by%20Psyiconic%2C%20had%20a%20film%20based%20on%20his%20character%2C%20Terri%20Joe%2C%20debut%20on%20the%20streamer%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223414%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kinigra%20Deon%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2066512e5a80cfe0502d9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222561%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKinigra%20Deon%3Cp%3EStefanie%20Keenan%2FThe%20Hollywood%20Reporter%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20%3Cstrong%3EMark%20Phillips%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20who%20built%20a%20comedy%20un