rget%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erichly%20valued%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20start%20looking%20elsewhere%20for%20deals%2C%20says%20investing%20legend%20Rob%20Arnott.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-stock-outlook-rob-arnott-nasdaq-sp500-index-inclusion-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EArnott%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Research%20Affiliates%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20recommend%20dumping%20growth%20shares%20all%20at%20once%2C%20but%20rather%2C%20thinks%20investors%20should%20start%20whittling%20their%20exposure%20while%20looking%20toward%20other%20unloved%20corners%20of%20the%20market.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20be%20worried%20about%20being%20complacent%20about%20a%20market%20that's%20as%20expensive%20as%20it%20is%20today%2C%20but%20I'd%20also%20be%20worried%20about%20bailing%20out%20too%20aggressively%2C%26quot%3B%20Arnott%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20best%20course%20for%20investors%20is%20to%20just%20gradually%20average%20their%20exposure%20to%20US%20and%20especially%20US%20growth%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20average%20it%20down%20over%20the%20course%20of%20months%2C%20even%20over%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20and%20pivot%20that%20money%20into%20the%20segments%20of%20the%20market%20that%20are%20cheap.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20area%20of%20the%20market%20is%20small-cap%20value%20stocks%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-stock-outlook-rob-arnott-nasdaq-sp500-index-inclusion-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EArnott%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20is%20a%20pioneer%20in%20alternative%20index%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20particular%20corner%20of%20the%20market%20overlaps%20with%20two%20factors%20that%20find%20themselves%20in%20historically%20cheap%20territory.%20For%20one%2C%20small-cap%20valuations%20relative%20to%20large-caps%20are%20uber%20cheap%2C%20said%20Arnott%2C%20calling%20the%20spread%20between%20the%20two%20groups%20%26quot%3Benormous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20April%20study%20published%20by%20Fidelity%20looking%20at%20data%20since%201990%2C%20when%20small-cap%20valuations%20are%20in%20their%20cheapest%20quintile%20relative%20to%20large-cap%20valuations%2C%20small-caps%20outperform%20large-caps%20over%20the%20following%2010-year%20period%2096%25%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20factor%20is%20value%20versus%20growth.%20The%20two%20groups'%20valuations%20are%20at%20their%20largest%20ever%20spread%2C%20as%20shown%20in%20the%20chart%20below%20from%20Yardeni%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222628%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22value%20vs%20growth%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a207f202ab5f9757add8e1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221478%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EYardeni%20Research%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20put%20on%20finer%20point%20on%20just%20how%20extreme%20things%20have%20gotten%2C%20Arnott%20dropped%20an%20eye-popping%20stat%3A%20there%20are%20now%20seven%20individual%20companies%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20that%20alone%20have%20a%20larger%20market%20capitalization%20than%20the%20entire%20Russell%202000%20value%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20precedent%20for%20that%2C%20and%20that's%20how%20stretched%20the%20market%20has%20become%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20cheap%20area%20where%20investors%20can%20find%20opportunities%2C%20Arnott%20said%2C%20is%20in%20emerging-market%20value%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chart%20below%20from%20Research%20Affiliates%20shows%20that%20emerging%20market%20stocks%20are%20cheaper%20relative%20to%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20than%2080%25%20of%20the%20time%20since%201996.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22EM%20stocks%20vs%20sp500%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a207f072e5a80cfe050330c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22992%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20Affiliates%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20can%20gain%20exposure%20to%20these%20trades%20through%20funds%20like%20the%20iShares%20Russell%202000%20Value%20ETF%20(IWN)%20and%20the%20Avantis%20Emerging%20Markets%20Value%20ETF%20(AVES).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-stock-picks-value-growth-emerging-markets-investing-rob-arnott-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780564801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a207ff92ab5f9757add8e26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-stock-picks-value-growth-emerging-markets-investing-rob-arnott-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20richly%20valued%20market%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20start%20slowly%20weaning%20off%20the%20US%20growth%20trade%2C%20says%20investing%20legend%20Rob%20Arnott.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vickrum%20Digwa%2C%20father%20and%20brother%20appear%20in%20court%20over%20weapons%20charges%20day%20after%20murder%20sentence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780564459000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131501736%2Cimgsize-940065.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fvickrum-digwa-father-and-brother-appear-in-court-over-weapons-charges-day-after-murder-sentence%2Farticleshow%2F131501478.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131501478.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3