igcaption%3EUber%20is%20pulling%20back%20recruiting%20efforts%20in%20some%20cities%20as%20robotaxis%20roll%20out%2C%20CEO%20Dara%20Khosrowshahi%20said.%3Cp%3EMyung%20J.%20Chun%20%2F%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUber%20is%20recruiting%20fewer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdriven-for-uber-decade-dont-know-what-my-future-holds-2025-10%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eride-hailing%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20some%20cities%2C%20CEO%20Dara%20Khosrowshahi%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20pullback%20comes%20as%20self-driving%20cars%20from%20companies%20like%20Waymo%20become%20more%20common.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKhosrowshahi%20said%20that%20the%20move%20is%20meant%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20existing%20drivers%20to%20earn%20on%20the%20app.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAutomation%20is%20finally%20coming%20for%20the%20human%20rideshare%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20is%20cutting%20back%20on%20recruiting%20drivers%20in%20cities%20where%20autonomous%20vehicles%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-waymo-partnership-relationship-hybrid-market-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elike%20those%20from%20Waymo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20operating%2C%20CEO%20Dara%20Khosrowshahi%20told%20Fast%20Company%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fastcompany.com%2F91548707%2Fuber-robotaxi-strategy-dara-khosrowshahi%3Fmvgt%3DJurXL7o6elCr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0published%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20fewer%20new%20entrants%20in%20those%20markets%20ensures%20%26quot%3Bthat%20the%20drivers%20who%20are%20%5Balready%5D%20in-market%2C%20who%20are%20experienced%2C%20and%20who've%20been%20with%20us%20through%20this%20whole%20journey%20continue%20to%20earn%2C%26quot%3B%20Khosrowshahi%20told%20the%20magazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20provide%20evidence%20of%20what%20some%20ride-hailing%20drivers%20have%20long%20feared%3A%20The%20spread%20of%20robotaxis%20will%20mean%20fewer%20opportunities%20for%20them%20to%20earn%20a%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20all%20bad%20news%20for%20rideshare%20drivers%2C%20however.%20Uber%20says%20that%20while%20it's%20recruiting%20fewer%20drivers%2C%20it's%20seen%20more%20drivers%20sign%20up%20as%20demand%20for%20the%20service%20grows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhosrowshahi%20said%20that%20human%20drivers%20in%20markets%20where%20Uber%20has%20added%20driverless%20cars%2C%20such%20as%20Atlanta%20and%20Austin%2C%20are%20busier%20than%20their%20counterparts%20in%20cities%20without%20the%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrivers%20in%20those%20cities%20are%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20more%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Khosrowshahi%20said%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BInvest%20Like%20the%20Best%26quot%3B%20podcast%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20number%20of%20drivers%20joining%20the%20platform%20is%20increasing%2C%20because%20it%20looks%20like%20AVs%20are%20actually%20adding%20incremental%20demand%20to%20the%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20autonomous%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Uber%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20both%20of%20Khosrowshahi's%20statements%20%26quot%3Bcan%20be%20true%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20the%20company%20is%20reducing%20its%20marketing%20spending%20in%20some%20cities%20while%20seeing%20more%20drivers%20sign%20up%20for%20Uber%20on%20their%20own%20as%20they%20respond%20to%20increased%20rider%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20robotaxis%2C%20Uber%20says%20it%20will%20still%20need%20human%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobotaxis-change-role-of-human-drivers-uber-chief-says-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAndrew%20Macdonald%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Uber's%20COO%2C%20said%20last%20year%20that%20the%20number%20of%20Uber%20drivers