C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20worked%20really%2C%20really%20hard%20on%20figuring%20out%3A%20What%20is%20that%20life%20force%20behind%20the%20eyes%3F%20How%20can%20we%20create%20that%3F%20How%20can%20we%20duplicate%20that%20so%20that%20the%20characters%20are%20believable%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20viewers%20prefer%20AI%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-launches-a-new-micro-drama-app-called-pinedrama-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok's%20PineDrama%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20commenter%20described%20the%20AI%20actors%20as%20%26quot%3Bbetter%20than%20the%20human%20ones%26quot%3B%20in%20%26quot%3BSorry%20Ex-wife%2C%20I'm%20The%20Hidden%20Trillionaire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Teaser%20posters%20for%20the%20AI-generated%20micro%20dramas%20%26quot%3BBound%20by%20Fire%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBloodbound%20Luna%26quot%3B%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a20415f2e5a80cfe0502bff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVerticals%20platforms%20Shortical%20and%20Vigloo%20announced%20fully%20AI-generated%20shows%20earlier%20this%20year.%3Cp%3EShortical%2FVigloo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20aren't%20so%20sure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20commenter%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Hoodie%20Hides%20a%20Fortune%26quot%3B%20wrote%20that%20AI-generated%20stories%20are%20%26quot%3Breally%20getting%20out%20of%20hand%20these%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea281f57-d29e-42b1-a251-220edefefcca%5C%22%3E'There%20for%20the%20humans'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20viewers%20will%20determine%20the%20future%20of%20AI%20in%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%201%2C670%20short-drama%20fans%20who%20responded%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.co