3B%20Lowery%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20seen%20so%20many%20actors%20and%20actresses%20that%20are%20so%20talented%20just%20move%20people%20in%20ways%20that%20robots%20can%20never%20do%20and%20AI%20can%20never%20replicate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20performers%2C%20like%20Manning%2C%20have%20millions%20of%20followers%20on%20social%20media%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20promote%20shows%20in%20ways%20a%20synthetic%20actor%20can't.%20The%20actor%20regularly%20posts%20behind-the-scenes%20photos%20and%20videos%20from%20set%20to%20tease%20shows%20via%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20cool%20to%20see%20how%20many%20people%20we%20have%20on%20our%20side%20that%20want%20us%20to%20succeed%20and%20that%20push%20us%20every%20single%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Manning%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsabel%20Dr%C3%A9an%2C%20a%20micro-drama%20producer%2C%20said%20she%20receives%20%26quot%3Bdaily%26quot%3B%20requests%20from%20apps%20to%20make%20AI-generated%20films.%20She%20said%20the%20industry's%20greatest%20challenge%20is%20the%20high%20cost%20of%20marketing%20the%20micro%20dramas%2C%20which%20AI%20actors%20would%20not%20help%20solve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22491f3f58-3a1f-406f-8e59-901a5837293d%5C%22%3EA%20sign%20of%20things%20to%20come%20for%20Hollywood%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAre%20movie%20stars%20the%20next%20target%20for%20AI%20disruption%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHollywood%20studios%20have%20been%20wrestling%20with%20how%20to%20leverage%20AI's%20benefits%20without%20upsetting%20the%20creative%20community%20or%20alienating%20viewers.%20Some%20are%20using%20the%20technology%20in%20limited%20ways%2C%20such%20as%20to%20de-age%20characters%2C%20while%20others%20are%20making%20deeper%20bets%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2Fcolumn%2F930118%2Fnetflix-gen-ai-animation-inkubator%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eareas%20like%20animation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENikola%20Todorovic%2C%20an%20artist%20and%20cofounder%20of%20the%20VFX%20studio%20Wonder%20Dynamics%2C%20said%20his%20company%20uses%20AI%20and%20other%20tools%20to%20generate%20natural-looking%20crowd%20scenes%20and%20to%20design%20realistic%2C%20non-human%20characters%20that%20don't%20exist%20in%20real%20life%20(think%20%26quot%3BPlanet%20of%20the%20Apes%26quot%3B).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20has%20its%20limits%2C%20Todorovic%20said.%20AI-generated%20video%20doesn't%20allow%20for%20the%20necessary%20tweaking%20of%20motion%20and%20emotional%20details%20that%20are%20hard%20to%20prompt%2C%20for%20instance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-media-container%3D%5C%22image%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22img%5C%22%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-figure-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-content-type%3D%5C%22image%2Fjpeg%5C%22%20data-srcs%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2039412ab5f9757add86fa%26quot%3B%3A%7B%26quot%3BcontentType%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bimage%2Fjpeg%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioW%26quot%3B%3A4160%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioH%26quot%3B%3A5200%7D%7D%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2039412ab5f9757add86fa%3Fwidth%3D1300%26format%3Djpeg%26auto%3Dwebp%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Luke%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%5Cn%3Cfigcaption%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-caption%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-source%5C%22%3E%5CnAdam%20Amengual%20for%20BI%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20tech%20improves%20to%20the%20point%20where%20it%20can%20more%20effectively%20mimic%20actors'%20work%2C%20it%20would%20likely%20draw%20renewed%20backlash.%20When%20AI%20character%20Tilly%20Norwood%20came%20on%20the%20scene%20in%202025%20through%20a%20short%20film%20and%20Instagram%20account%2C%20SAG-AFTRA%20and%20several%20of%20its%20famous%20members%20decried%20her%20creation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20actor%20outrage%20may%20not%20be%20enough%20to%20slow%20down%20Hollywood%20executives%20eager%20to%20cut%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryn%20Mooser%2C%20CEO%20of%20Asteria%20Film%2C%20an%20AI-driven%20film%20studio%2C%20said%20he%20expects%20%26quot%3Bexponential%20growth%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20use%20of%20synthetic%20humans%2C%20noting%20the%20spread%20of%20AI%20avatars%20in%20China%20who%20sell%20things%20online.%20He%20sees%20Hollywood%20using%20AI%20to%20create%20minor%20characters%20or%20those%20whose%20faces%20aren't%20visible%2C%20but%20believes%20the%20industry%20isn't%20close%20to%20replacing%20movie%20and%20TV%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20world%20where%20Tilly%20Norwood%20is%20made%20for%20an%20Avengers%20movie%20is%20far%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20corners%2C%20it's%20AI%20or%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Pearce%2C%20an%20LA-based%20producer%20who%20makes%20verticals%2C%20said%20that%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20at%20least%20three%20platforms%20had%20told%20him%20they%20were%20pausing%20live-action%20production%20and%20shifting%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClients%20are%20telling%20me%2C%20'We're%20not%20doing%20any%20shows%20that%20aren't%20AI%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20compete.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Factors-losing-jobs-to-ai-hollywood-micro-drama-industry-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780563901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2033a42e5a80cfe0502b80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Factors-losing-jobs-to-ai-hollywood-micro-drama-industry-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actors%20who%20flocked%20to%20the%20booming%20mic