tors-126060400594_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former%20Google%20distinguished%20engineer%20says%20AI%20isn't%20replacing%20software%20engineers%20%E2%80%94%20just%20ones%20who%20only%20know%20how%20to%20code%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224222%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kelsey%20Hightower%20attends%20the%202025%20RenderATL%20Tech%20Conference%20at%20AmericasMart%20Atlanta%20on%20June%2013%2C%202025%20in%20Atlanta%2C%20Georgia.%20(Photo%20by%20Derek%20White%2FGetty%20Images)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a2095962ab5f9757add8eef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222815%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKelsey%20Hightower%20emphasizes%20the%20importance%20of%20diverse%20skills%20beyond%20coding%20in%20software%20engineering.%3Cp%3EDerek%20White%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKelsey%20Hightower%20emphasizes%20the%20importance%20of%20diverse%20skills%20beyond%20coding%20in%20software%20engineering.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHightower%20said%20that%20AI%20separates%20those%20who%20can%20only%20code%20and%20those%20who%20can%20make%20good%20decisions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20is%20growing%20sentiment%20that%20taste%2C%20communication%20and%20relationship-building%20are%20AI-proof%20skills.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20may%20be%20changing%20software%20engineering%2C%20but%20former%20Google%20distinguished%20engineer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-kelsey-hightower-self-taught-developer-kubernetes-cloud-computing-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKelsey%20Hightower%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20developers%20who%20bring%20more%20than%20coding%20skills%20to%20the%20table%20have%20little%20reason%20to%20panic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20Wednesday's%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Pragmatic%20Engineer%2C%26quot%3B%20Hightower%20told%20show%20host%20Gergely%20Orosz%20that%20AI%20is%20exposing%20a%20long-standing%20divide%20between%20developers%20who%20only%20write%20code%20and%20those%20who%20contribute%20across%20product%2C%20design%2C%20architecture%2C%20and%20business%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20as%20a%20software%20developer%2C%20you%20may%20have%20thought%20your%20job%20was%20to%20be%20the%20only%20person%20in%20organization%20that%20can%20write%20code.%20And%20since%20no%20one%20else%20could%20do%20it%2C%20you%20were%20safe%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20you%20probably%20made%20more%20money%20than%20everybody%2C%20and%20you%20were%20fine%20with%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20you%20didn't%20learn%20any%20other%20skills%20%E2%80%94%20networking%2C%20product%20management%2C%20design%2C%20talking%20to%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20Hightower%20added.%20%26quot%3BNow%20you%20got%20caught.%20The%20only%20thing%20you%20were%20good%20at%20is%20now%20been%20commoditized.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20comments%20echo%20a%20growing%20sentiment%20across%20Silicon%20Valley%20that%20judgment%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fethan-mollick-ai-expert-wharton-taste-skills-ai-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esometimes%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Btaste%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20is%20becoming%20a%20key%20differentiator%20as%20AI%20becomes%20more%20proficient%20at%20executing%20tasks.%20Recent%20discussions%20among%20tech%20leaders%2C%20including%20Y%20Combinator%20cofounder%20Paul%20Graham%20and%20OpenAI%20president%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaste-new-core-skill-ai-debate-memes-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGreg%20Brockman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20centered%20on%20the%20idea%20that%20choosing%20what%20to%20build%20may%20matter%20more%20than%20the%20mechanics%20of%20building%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalesforce%20CEO%20Marc%20Benioff%20and%20Duolingo%20CEO%20Luis%20von%20Ahn%20also%20recently%20said%20that%20AI%20couldn't%20replace%20certain%20jobs%20at%20their%20companies%2C%20because%20it%20is%20hard%20to%20automate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmo-gawdat-google-most-valuable-skill-in-the-ai-era-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eskills%20in%20communication%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20relationship-building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHightower%20told%20Orosz%20later%20in%20the%20interview%20that%20software%20engineering%20is%20increasingly%20evolving%20into%20a%20discipline%20of%20making%20decisions%2C%20where%20%26quot%3Bwriting%20is%20thinking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20full-stack%20engineer%2C%20you're%20probably%20like%2C%20man%2C%20there's%20so%20much%20more%20than%20just%20writing%20code%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20loves%20%26quot%3BClaude%20because%20now%20I%20can%20focus%20on%20those%20things%2C%20and%20I%20can%20use%20these%20tools%20instead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkelsey-hightower-google-ai-replacing-enigeers-only-coding-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780563181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a20986db4fb977f35984348%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkelsey-hightower-google-ai-replacing-enigeers-only-coding-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kelsey%20Hightower%20said%20that%20AI%20is%20replacing%20those%20who%20can%20only%20code%2C%20but%20not%20engineers%20who%20have%20diverse%20skills%20sets%20and%20good%20judgment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22katherineli%40insider.com%20(Katherine%20Li)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Another%20Trinamool%20Mayor%20Quits%20As%20Crisis%20Deepens%20For%20Mamata%20Banerjee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22A%20long-time%20associate%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%20supremo%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Krishna%20Chak